I"Ü$<p><a target="_blank" href="https://www.altcointrading.net/img/xmr/monero-cli-1.jpg" title="AltcoinTrading.NET - How to setup Monero core wallet (for dummies)"><figure class="border"><amp-img itemprop="image" src="https://www.altcointrading.net/img/xmr/monero-cli-1.jpg" alt="How to setup Monero core wallet (for dummies)" title="AltcoinTrading.NET - How to setup Monero core wallet (for dummies)" layout="responsive" width="700px" height="360px"></amp-img></figure></a></p>

<p><em>Image: Monero CLI wallet is the only reasonable and well tested option to store larger amount of XMR. A graphical wallet (GUI) is out too and working though. Itâ€™s probably safe but it is beta and itâ€™s always safer to wait some time with new releases to get them tested.</em></p>

<hr />

<div class="clearfix adfix"><amp-iframe width="728px" height="90px" layout="responsive" data-aa="147076" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-modals allow-popups allow-forms" src="https://ad.a-ads.com/147076?size=728x90"><amp-img layout="fill" src="/img/ads/ad-placeholder.jpg" placeholder=""></amp-img></amp-iframe></div>
